		{"id":"55345bc9286de900","type":"text","text":"2","x":-8145,"y":4390,"width":70,"height":60,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"16c8581daaa9b25f","type":"text","text":"4","x":-8075,"y":4390,"width":70,"height":60,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"aa3a1505227d53d2","type":"text","text":"JUDGMENT","x":-7918,"y":5280,"width":250,"height":60,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"4150eab3ac692b66","type":"text","text":"The card blazes in your hand, radiant and commanding, a clarion call of change and reckoning.  \nThe streets roar with the cries of the people. The Jester’s schemes ignite a revolution, and the kingdom trembles beneath the weight of its own corruption.  \nThe walls crumble, the banners fall, and those who were silenced now rise.","x":-7915,"y":5440,"width":245,"height":615},
		{"id":"10c23b0f37a68d11","type":"text","text":"HAND OF THE KING II","x":-9320,"y":4390,"width":250,"height":60,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"8f19fa9767d52979","type":"text","text":"2","x":-9015,"y":4390,"width":70,"height":60,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"268ea91310ab48d6","type":"text","text":"1","x":-9015,"y":4270,"width":70,"height":60,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"966d697e2e191f8e","type":"text","text":"THE FOOL REVERSED","x":-7835,"y":3085,"width":250,"height":60,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"82ae3eb4e33c9d20","type":"text","text":"HAND OF THE KING I","x":-9320,"y":4270,"width":250,"height":60,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"96ce5dc7d039c695","type":"text","text":"The card falls heavy in your hand, a dark mirror of inevitability.  \nYou failed to produce the visions the king demanded. Your gift, once a spark of hope, is now deemed a failure.  \nAs the wedding unfolds, you are brought forward, not as a guest, but as a spectacle. Fire consumes you, the smoke rising through the halls of the palace, a grim warning to all who dare defy the king’s will.","x":-6823,"y":5440,"width":245,"height":675},
		{"id":"5695842f1102ef3f","type":"text","text":"The card falls heavy in your hand, a dark mirror of inevitability.  \nYou failed to produce the visions the king demanded. Your gift, once a spark of hope, is now deemed a failure.  \nAs the wedding unfolds, you are brought forward, not as a guest, but as a spectacle. Fire consumes you, the smoke rising through the halls of the palace, a grim warning to all who dare defy the king’s will.\nThe Jester watches as the flames engulf you, his laughter gone, replaced by grim understanding. With you, every last hope for a revolution is burning, leaving only ash where change might have begun.","x":-6468,"y":5440,"width":245,"height":675},
		{"id":"b10ecde9436cca13","type":"text","text":"The card quivers in your hand, brimming with restless energy.  \nIts laughter is sharper now, daring and reckless, no longer just a whisper but a call to action.  \nYou feel the Fool’s spirit surge—mischievous and clever, yes, but now unstoppable, driven to stir the streets and ignite the people’s fury.  \nChaos is no longer a game; it is a plan, precise and urgent.  \nThe Fool Reversed urges you forward: the spark is lit, the time to act has come.","x":-7835,"y":3185,"width":250,"height":615},
		{"id":"f7c2b691df45ae3e","type":"text","text":"THE HIEROPHANT","x":-7540,"y":3085,"width":250,"height":60,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"1e3e0a9ad326a3b6","type":"text","text":"The card stands solemn in your hand, a symbol of authority, law, and unquestioned order.  \nIts presence is heavy, commanding obedience and adherence to tradition.  \nYou feel the Hand of the King in its weight—stern, unyielding, and intolerant of delay or disobedience.  \nEvery instruction, every glance, carries the authority of the realm.  \nThe Hierophant reminds you that some powers demand respect and compliance, and that rules govern even the smallest actions in the kingdom.","x":-7540,"y":3185,"width":250,"height":615},
		{"id":"26ab8ad769fd9057","type":"text","text":"THE HIEROPHANT REVERSED","x":-7255,"y":3085,"width":250,"height":60,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"0f745eebdeb7c366","type":"text","text":"WHEEL OF FORTUNE","x":-9340,"y":3085,"width":250,"height":60,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"e6ba6ee05cf75a04","type":"text","text":"The card spins in your hand, its surface shimmering with chance and uncertainty.  \nThe wheel turns, indifferent to your efforts, and fate moves as it will.  \nThe Wheel of Fortune reminds you that some things cannot be forced. Sometimes, you must wait, watch, and let destiny reveal its course.  \nThe future is in motion, and every choice, or lack of it, carries its own consequence.","x":-9340,"y":3185,"width":250,"height":615},
		{"id":"6fa1dd474a504674","type":"text","text":"Everything is ready.  \nSoon it will all begin.  \nThe revolution shall be glorious, and at last we will be free.","x":1600,"y":4140,"width":250,"height":180},
		{"id":"4a1eec967b3ae17f","type":"text","text":"I am the Head of the Royal Guard.  \nMy life stands beneath those of royal blood, whom I shall protect until my last breath.","x":2215,"y":3120,"width":250,"height":220},
		{"id":"9bc96975a8b91fd3","type":"text","text":"Who am I?  \nI am the princess, soon to become the queen of this realm.  \nIt is the destiny chosen for me, and my duty commands that I obey.","x":1925,"y":3120,"width":250,"height":220},
		{"id":"a7cb2b78142464e2","type":"text","text":"Princess","x":1925,"y":2860,"width":250,"height":60,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"ecc226ba29061fa9","type":"text","text":"Guard","x":2215,"y":2860,"width":250,"height":60,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"354cbac52c50da40","type":"text","text":"I must go now.  \nI must find my love.  \nThank you… for everything.","x":1925,"y":4140,"width":250,"height":180},
		{"id":"d7e215c661a1630a","type":"text","text":"We must flee before the afternoon.  \nThere is no turning back now.","x":2215,"y":4140,"width":250,"height":180},
		{"id":"64766e173955a365","type":"text","text":"The wedding bells are ringing.  \nI must prepare myself, for this day will set me upon the path of my destiny.","x":1925,"y":3870,"width":250,"height":180},
		{"id":"b12cd526fb98372f","type":"text","text":"...The princess is to be married today.  \nI have much work to attend to.","x":2215,"y":3870,"width":250,"height":180},
		{"id":"2e31fd2b39ad1682","type":"text","text":"How many merry people are here today.  \nLaughing, dancing… and I shall be working until dawn.","x":1600,"y":3870,"width":250,"height":180},
		{"id":"52a390e9f6ea74b5","type":"text","text":"I could not sleep tonight. The screams from the dungeon were too loud.  \nThe prince… he…  \n_sighs_","x":1925,"y":3500,"width":250,"height":180},
		{"id":"9ef46938d89da9ec","type":"text","text":"My duty is to protect the realm, not to indulge in gossip.","x":2215,"y":3500,"width":250,"height":180},
		{"id":"935f827ba35ec020","type":"text","text":"I am the Hand, commanded by the King to serve the realm.","x":1300,"y":3120,"width":250,"height":180},
		{"id":"c6e3a61bba1b924b","type":"text","text":"Hand Of the King","x":1300,"y":2860,"width":250,"height":60,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"04667ba54e5c0a76","type":"text","text":"I have no time for you—the wedding is today","x":1300,"y":3870,"width":250,"height":180},
		{"id":"d58601c289ae1659","type":"text","text":"Do not disturb me in my work.","x":1300,"y":3500,"width":250,"height":180},
		{"id":"3f4749f423175cc1","type":"text","text":"I am the Fool, employed by our gracious king to amuse and distract the court.  \nI am the jester, the clown—made for laughter and obedience.","x":1605,"y":3120,"width":250,"height":180},
		{"id":"afa8eefc6b7e05f7","type":"text","text":"Fool","x":1605,"y":2860,"width":250,"height":60,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"f985cab9321ed397","type":"text","text":"The court will soon be dancing, and I shall be there to entertain them.  \nSuch is my cross to bear.","x":1605,"y":3500,"width":250,"height":180},
		{"id":"b1a26460f22871bb","x":-9170,"y":2536,"width":250,"height":60,"type":"text","text":"TEST TEST TEST"}
	],
